### ID生成服务测试（号段模式）

### 生成编码 - 按日（yyyyMMdd）- 首次调用自动初始化
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "OR",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}

### 生成编码 - 按日（yyyyMMdd）- 第二次调用
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "OR",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}

### 生成编码 - 按年月日时分秒（yyyyMMddHHmmss）- 高并发推荐
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "OR",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMddHHmmss"
}

### 生成编码 - 按月（yyyyMM）- 低频次业务
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "EM",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMM"
}

### 生成编码 - 按年（yyyy）- 极低频次业务（谨慎使用）
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "AG",
  "datePattern": "yyyy"
}

### 错误测试 - 前缀为空
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}

### 错误测试 - 前缀格式错误
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "ord",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}

### 错误测试 - 不支持的日期格式
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "OR",
  "datePattern": "MMdd"
}

### 并发测试 - 快速生成多个编码（验证号段模式）
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "TS",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}

### 不同业务前缀隔离测试
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "OD",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}

###
POST http://localhost:8085/inner/api/v1/idgen/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prefix": "PY",
  "datePattern": "yyyyMMdd"
}
